data.description: ***  Price improvement  ***                                                    Lovely, low maintenance and completely move-in ready! This home offers tons of upgrades, including laminate hardwood floors, heavy crown molding, wainscoting and 2" Blinds throughout. The large kitchen has extended dining with granite, tile backsplash, recessed lights, black appliances, & music port with 2 built-in ceiling speakers. Enjoy the outdoors with a lovely Screened-In Porch with Ceiling Fan mount and Wood Privacy Fence. Custom wood Stairs lead to the bright owner's Suite with a Double Vanity, Separate Shower and large walk-in closet.  Two additional bedrooms upstairs share a hall bath. Minutes to Fort Jackson, McEntire AFB, Shaw and convenient to shopping and dinning.  Make your appointment today!
